\id 1PE Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h 1 Pita
\toc1 Khe Pita Fhara Khergi Gap
\toc2 1 Pita
\toc3 1 Pi
\mt1 1 PITA
\mt2 Khe Pita Fhara Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Pita kha gava khergiap, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, simt…®gi bak…®vi ndi gumgi gu mbigi ndi mbarigi. Ana ana kherav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde Zisas Kraisan buna vhuueŇč, nde taagi ne nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Zisas rimgiap taagia khavgi. Ana khavgiap, Fhe Bak…®me han Hevenan ndav, khaŇč suaŇčgi, ana taagi zir…®rga.‚ÄĚ Mbe mba ana suaŇčgi kameŇč nd…®knd…®g…®p, ana rarg…® k…®rim, ana taagi zir…®rga.
\ip Mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe guigira simt…®gi ndi. Mba simt…®gi, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gir mpari simt…®gi ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip guigira Zisas khoth…®g…® thivgiv, havhargip, Ňčg…®v k…®rim, Zisas taagi zir…®rga. Mba tugen, mbe ne suaŇčv vheza vhuuŇč guarara ndigirga.
\c 1
\ms1 Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčv, mba ndirga bigir vhuuin rarg…®p wari k…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2 T 1.15; Ze 1.1\x*Gu Pita Krais Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara guma mbe ma. Gu kha gava khergiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi gumgi gu mbigi, gu anan nde ndi mbai. Nde mba tamtam fhura harigi Ňčguir mba Pontus Ňčgu bak…®me gum, Garesia Ňčgu bak…®me, Kapadosia Ňčgu bak…®me, Esia Ňčgu bak…®me gum, Bitinia Ňčgu bak…®me, nde ntan ki. Gu kha gava khergiap nde ndi mbai.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ro 1.7; 8.29; 2 Te 2.13; Hi 10.22; 12.24; 2 Pi 1.2\x*Fhe Bak…®me fhum wo vuzvugar ana nden won mbuigim, nde ana gumgi gu mbigira ki. Ana Ňäina Ňäaar nden kurkurigim, nde za wari won ruru t…®vi gum bigi ndiv, zam anan n…®…®Ňčgiap, ana n…®man Ňčgarav ki. Nde Ňčgarav k…®v, nde tuituigip Zisas Kraisan buni vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…®rim, ana v…®z…®n nde ruarim, nde Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®rga. Fhe Bak…®men kora muumbar khaŇč t…®g…®p nde phorg…® k…®rim, nde ndavi mb…®rav, wari k…®ri.
\s1 K…®r…® t…®var vhuuŇč nza garav, Hevenan mbur ki.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1 Ko 15.20; 2 Ko 1.3; Ef 1.3; Ze 1.18\x*Nza ne suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuarga. Ana Fhe Bak…®me ma, ana nza Bak…®me Zisas Kraisan Ndia ma. Ana guigira kora muumbara bak…®me nzan kav, ana taagia Zisas Krais khavgi. Ana mba tuavar, ana k…®r…® t…®v gum ruru kaman nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Mba k…®r…® t…®v gum rurur kam nzan havhargirim, nza k…®v, ana mba nzan n…®…®n za suaŇčgi bigir vhuuin rarg…®p wari k…®rga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Kor 1.5; 1.12; 2 T 4.8; Ze 5.4\x*Ana Hevenan mpirmpir…®gar vhuuŇč, ndir zav nzan farasegi. Mba mpirmpir…®gar vhuuŇč ana mbat…®girga fhu. Mba mpirmpir…®k, ana Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man Ňčgarigi. Mba mpirmpir…®gar vhuuŇč, anan vh…®zgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®me mba mpirmpir…®ga vhuuŇč, ana ana bevahegim, ana Hevenan mbur ki. Nde ana phorg…®p Hevenan k…®v, mba mpirmpir…®ga vhuuŇč ndigip, k…®rga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Zo 10.28-29; 17.11-15; Zu 1.1\x*Nde Krais khoth…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me won ŇčkasŇčkar nde garim, nde nzerara k…®rga. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, ana taagi nde ndigirim, nde guigira nzerara k…®rga. Ana mba nden muun zav mbui bigeŇč, ne Zisas taagi kha nuianan zir…®rga, ne za k…®rar h…®g…®rga.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ro 12.12; 2 Ko 4.17; 6.10; Ze 1.2; 1 Pi 5.10\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me nden muun za mbui bigeŇč, nde ne nd…®knd…®gap ndikndigi. Nde ntigem kha tuga t…®v…®nera, mbark…®rga mparmparei nden h…®v, simt…®gi gu zaagir nden n…®…®nga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Jop 23.10; Sng 66.10; Snd 17.3; Ais 48.10; Sek 13.9; Mal 3.3; Ro 2.7; 2.10; Ze 1.3\x*Mba t…®vi nden him, Fhe Bak…®me nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k, ana anan mpari. Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, gor, ana guigira big…®na vhuuŇč guar ma. Mbe fhara anan mparav, ana tui, ana gor guar o, fhu. Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k, ana guigira gor kambarav, guigira big…®na vhuuŇč ma. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, gor, ana mbar…®gi big…®n ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mbark…®rga mparmparei nden h…®rga, nta khuen nde kh…®vi, nde guigira Krais khoth…®gi. Nde zumgum Zisas Krais taagi zir…®p za k…®rar h…®rga tugar, ana guigira nden ndikndig…®p, nde z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuav, z…® bak…®men nden n…®…®nga.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Zo 20.29; 2 Ko 5.7; Hi 11.1; 11.27; 1 Zo 4.20\x*Nde ana gangi fhuvara, nde ana vuzvugiap wari won ndavir ana nd…®…®i. Nde vh…®ra ana gari fhu, nde ana khoth…®gap, anan ndikndigi. Nde anan ndikndigi ndikndik, ana guigira za kha nuianan ndikndigi kambarigi. Nza kamthoon za mba ndikndiga bun suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ro 6.22\x*Fhe Bak…®me taagia nde ndi ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde Krais khoth…®gi.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Dan 2.44; Hag 2.7; Sek 6.12; Mt 13.16-17; 2 Pi 1.19-21\x*Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi, mbe ntigem Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgi bigi, mbe nta bun nzuai. Mbe khaŇč t…®gap Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, Fhe Bak…®me taagia nde ndigi kama n…®…®eŇč ga nzuav gari.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Sng 22; Ais 53; Ru 24.26-27; 1 Pi 3.19; 2 Pi 1.21\x*Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar, Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgir vhen kav, ana mbe rugim, mbe mba Krais ndirga simt…®gi, mbe nta bun nzuai. Ana mba simt…®gi ndigip, ana zumgum z…® bak…®me ndigirga. Mba Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi vh…®ra khueŇč nzuav nzai, ‚ÄúMba taagia nza ndirga guma, ana ras…® tugar h…®g…®rie? Thag…®na big…®n mba tugar h…®g…®rie?‚ÄĚ
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Dan 9.24; Ef 3.10; Hi 11.13; 11.39-40\x*Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®me khuen mbe kh…®vigi, mba bigi nta nduarira wari won tuga sarav heg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe Fhe Bak…®me taagi nde ndirga kameŇč bun nzuaim, nde ne mbarara. Ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaara sarigim, ana Hevenan kegap zergim, ana ŇčkasŇčkar panan, gumgi ana buna vhuueŇč bun nzuav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nden muun zav suaŇčgi buneŇč, mbe ne bun suaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me enseri, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me nden muun za mbui bigeŇč kaŇčgirgane vuzvugi.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me Ňčgaravra k…®rgeŇč nzuav nzan kamgi.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Ru 12.35; Ro 13.13; 1 Ko 1.7; 1 Te 5.6-8\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nden nd…®knd…®gi zazera nd…®knd…®g…®p, nde tuituigira wari wo rui ruru t…®vi gan…®ri. Nde guigira khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Zisas khoth…®g…®ri. Zisas Krais za k…®rar h…®r…®m, Fhe Bak…®me nden muun za suaŇčgi bigen vhuueŇč nde nen rarga ki, ana mba bigen nden muunga.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ro 12.2; Ef 2.3; 4.17-18; 1 Te 4.5\x*Nde tari bigi mbararagi farar muuŇčgip bigi mbararari. Nde fhum, nd…®knd…®gi ki fhu, nde fhura mba nd…®knd…®gi gu vuzvugi mbat…®gi, nde nta z…®n vegi. Nde ntigem wom mba t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…® thari.
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Wkp 11.44-45; 19.2; 20.7; Mt 5.48; 2 Ko 7.1; Hi 12.14; 2 Pi 3.11\x*Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgi, ana Ňčgarav, ana vh…®ra t…®vir vhuuiŇčra mbui guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde wari ndiv, Fhe Bak…®men n…®…®Ňčgip, nden ruru t…®vi gu bigi Ňčgaravra k…®ri.
\v 16 Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Ňčgaravra k…®v t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, gu nde Fhe Bak…®me, gu Ňčgaravra ki.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me vheza bak…®men nza vhezgi.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Lo 10.17; Mt 6.9; FG 10.34; Ro 2.11; 2 Ko 5.6; 7.1; 2 T 4.14; Hi 11.13; 12.28; VB 2.23\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®men kaav, ‚ÄúDarar‚ÄĚ anan kaai. Mba Dara, ana nzan z…®ri ga nd…®knd…®gap, nza garap, nza nzuav nzuai fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana nza mbui t…®vi garav, nta nzuav nza nzuai. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde zazera ntige kha nuianan k…®v, nde khueŇč kaŇčgiri, kha nuian, ana guigira nzan Ňčgu guar fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde guigira Fhe Bak…®men piin k…®ri.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Ese 20.18; 1 Ko 6.20; 7.23; 1 Pi 4.3\x*Nde ntige kaŇčgi, nde fhum, nde wari won nz…®gi han ndigi t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde nta z…®n vegi. Fhe Bak…®me ntigem taagia nde vhezgiap, ana mba bigi t…®n nde ndigi. Ana nde ndigap, ana kha nuianan mbar…®gi bigi, gor gu sirva, ana ntan nde vhezgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Kis 12.5; Ais 53.7; Zo 1.29; 1.36; FG 20.28; 1 Ko 5.7; Hi 9.12-14; 1 Pi 1.2; VB 5.9\x*Ana Krais v…®z…®nra nde vhezgi. Mba v…®z…®n, ana guigira vhez vun ndagi v…®z…®n ma. Krais, ana sum kav, big…®na mp…®ga thaneŇč ki fhuv sipsiva Ňčguga fara muuŇčgi. \f a \fr 1:19 \ft Mbe IsreriŇč, mbe wari wo muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®z…®r zav, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčv, bigi ndia zav, mbe sipsivi vhuuiŇčra ndiav zav, Fhe Bak…®me nzuav ofari ga mbui. Ndu Wok Pris 22:17 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p, ves 25 th…®g…®ri. Pita mba t…®va nd…®knd…®gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKrais, ana guigira ofar muunga sipsivir vhuuŇč guar ma.‚ÄĚ \f*
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt FG 2.23; Ga 4.4; Ef 1.4; 1.10; Kor 1.26; Ta 1.2-3; Hi 9.26\x*Fhe Bak…®me zumgum kha nuiana muuŇčgi. Ana fhum guarara, ana taagi nde vhezgip, nde ndir zav, mba Ňčaarar muun zav, Zisas farasarav, mba Ňčaarar ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Kha mpuur rari vige h…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me nden kurkurar zav Krais ga sarigim, ana za k…®rar h…®gi.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Zo 14.6; FG 2.24; 2.33; Ro 4.24; 5.1-2; 10.9; Fi 2.9; Hi 2.9; 1 Pi 3.22\x*Ana k…®rar h…®gap, nden kurkurigim, nde Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi. Fhe Bak…®me Krais rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgiap, z…® bak…®men ana n…®…®Ňčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gap, ana nden n…®…®n za suaŇčgi bigi, nde ntan rarga ki.
\s1 Nza guigira wari won ndavir nza phorg…®p guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi n…®…®Ňčri.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Zo 13.34; FG 15.9; Ro 12.9-10; 1 T 1.5; 2 Pi 1.7; 1 Zo 3.18\x*Nde guigira buna guareŇč z…®n vui. Nde maaŇč mbuav, nde nduarira Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man Ňčgarav ki. Nde maaŇč mbuav, nde wari won ndavir nza phorg…®p guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i. Nde maaŇč mbui, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, guigira mbe vuzvug…®p, guigira wari won ndavir za mben n…®…®Ňčri.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Zo 1.13; Hi 4.12; Ze 1.18; 1 Zo 3.9\x*Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgim, nde niamuuŇč taagia nde tegi fara muuŇčgiap, nde gumgi gu mbigir Ňčkaa ki. Fhe Bak…®me won buna vhuueŇč ŇčkasŇčkar panan, ana nde muuŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ŇčkasŇčka ki. Ana mbara muuŇčgiap ki big…®na fara muuŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki. Ne guigira buna guareŇč ma. Nde ntigem, nde vh…®zi fhu Dara tari ma. Nzan ndegi gu nz…®gi, mbe za vh…®zi gumgi ma.
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Sng 103.15; Ais 51.12; Ze 1.10-11\x*\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Ais 40.6-8\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumgi gu mbigi, mbe tuga mpeen kha nuianan keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe vhaz…®gi fara muuŇčgiap vhemkora vh…®zi. Mbe z…® bak…®vi vhaz…®gi shivi fara muuŇčgiap fhura koskogav n…®…®eŇčri. Vhaz…®gi nz…®…®i, ntan shivi koskogav n…®…®eŇčri.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Zo 1.1; 1.14; 1 Zo 1.1-3\x*Fhe Bak…®me buneŇč, ne zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki.‚ÄĚ Mba buneŇč, mbe mba buna vhuueŇč, mbe ne bun nde suaŇčgi.
\c 2
\s1 Guma Bak…®me, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ki k…®man vhuuŇč ma.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Ef 4.22; 4.25; Kor 3.8; Hi 12.1; Ze 1.21\x*Nde ntigem t…®vir Ňčkaa ndigi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde mba t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde zam nta thav, nde mba bigi guiguigi t…®vi, nde vh…®ra nta thari. Nde vh…®ra fhura wari ga sh…®sh…®gi t…®vi, nde zam nta thari. Nde vh…®ra guma bigi vh…®rve kim, nde ana niihi t…®vi, nde vh…®ra nta thav, vh…®ra harigi gumgi z…®ri mbugum mbe nzuai t…®vi, nde vh…®ra nta thari.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Sng 34.8; Mt 18.3; Mk 10.15; 1 Ko 3.2; 14.20; Ef 4.15-16; Hi 5.12-13; 6.5\x*Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, niamuuŇč ntigera ruagi tar, ana guigira ta vuzvugi. Mba t…®vara, nde guigira Fhe Bak…®me han kega zi ta nde guigira ana vuzvugiri. Ana big…®na mbat…®ga the anan ki fhuvara. Mba khesharigi ta, ana nden ntuur kurkurigim, nta th…®g…® havhargip ŇčkasŇčkagip, Fhe Bak…®me nde n…®…®Ňčgi k…®r…® t…®var kama z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčv, zumgum Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p nzerara k…®rga.
\v 3 Nde Guma Bak…®me nza mbui t…®v, nde anan mparav, nde kaŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me t…®var vhuuŇčra nza mbui.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Sng 118.22; Ais 28.16; Mt 21.42; FG 4.11\x*Guma Bak…®me, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki k…®ma fara muuŇčgi, nde ana han z…®ri. Kha gumgi gu mbigi ana garim, ana big…®na mbat…®ga fhara muuŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana thav, ana fekh…®ngi. Fhe Bak…®me anan farasarav, ana garim, ana guigira big…®na vhuuŇč ma.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Kis 19.6; Ais 61.6; Hos 14.2; Mal 1.11; Ro 12.1; Ef 2.21-22; Fi 4.18; Hi 13.15-16; VB 1.6\x*Nde vh…®ra zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Ňčk…®…® ma. Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ŇčkasŇčkar panan, Fhe Bak…®me nden muuŇčgirim, nde anan phen k…®rga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgirga, Fhe Bak…®me nden faraseg…®rga, nde anan rotu gari gumgi k…®v, nde Zisas Krais z…®n panan, nde Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi ofa farar muuŇčgip, nde wari ndi Fhe Bak…®men n…®…®Ňčgirim, ana nde vuzvugirga.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Ais 28.16; Ro 9.33; Ef 2.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mbarara. Gu mba phenan muuŇčgirim, ana havhargirga k…®man vhuuŇč guarara, gu ana heav, ana ndi ndarigim, ana khar ki. Ana guigira k…®ma havharar vhuuŇč ma. Gu ana ndi fagim, ana Saion mb…®ksh…®man ki. Ana kaŇčgiap, ana khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe mem…®ra ndigirga tukt…®gi fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Sng 118.22; Mt 21.42; FG 4.11\x*Nde Krais khoth…®gi nt…®…®ri, Krais, ana guigira nden kurarga k…®man vhuuŇč ma. Mba ana khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúMba pheni ga mbui gumgi, mbe mba k…®ma gangiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAna k…®ma mbat…®k ma.‚Äô
\q1 Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgiap, ana phogia mbur kh…®ngi.
\q1 Mba k…®m, ana ntigem, ana fharav mba phena b…®na suirigim, ana havhargi.‚ÄĚ
\b
\m 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Ais 8.14-15; FG 4.11; Ro 9.22; 9.33; 1 Te 5.9\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba k…®m, ana vh…®ra mben tuav ga ndarigi k…®ma fara muuŇčgi. Mbe vh…®rvera mba k…®man savkor…®v, r…®v, mbar…®g…®rga.‚ÄĚ Mbe Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč daasui. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba k…®man savkorav wari ri. Fhe Bak…®me fhum suaŇčgi, mbe mba t…®var muunga.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Kis 19.5-6; Lo 4.20; 7.6; 14.2; Ais 9.2; 40.20-21; 43.20-21; Zo 17.19; FG 20.28; 26.18; Ef 5.8; Kor 1.13; Ta 2.14; 1 Pi 2.5\x*Fhe Bak…®me, ana nden farasegi, nde anan gumgi gu mbigi guari ma. Nde Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman panan rotu gari gumgi ma. Nde vh…®ra Ňčgarav Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi guari ma. Nde Fhe Bak…®me wora mbuigi gumgi gu mbigi ma. Nde, Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgi t…®vir vhuuiŇč guarira, nde nta bun suanga. Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgim, nde fhum kegi g…®ng…®n, nde ana thagim, ana nde ndigap won vhava Ňčaarar z…®gi. Mba vhavar Ňčaar, ana guigira vhavar Ňčaara vhuuŇč ma.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Hos 1.9-10; 2.23; Ro 9.25\x*Nde fhum gumgi gu mbigi kh…®ni kegi. Nde ntigem, nde Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi ki. Nde vh…®ra fhum, nde Fhe Bak…®me kora muumbara ndigi fhuvara. Nde ntigem, nde ana kora muumbara ndigi.
\ms1 Nza harigi gumgi gu mbigi r…®gar nza nzerara ruri.
\s1 Nza fhura Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara gumgi farar muuŇčgip wari k…®ri.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt 1 Sto 29.15; Sng 39.12; Ro 13.14; Ga 5.17; 5.24; Hi 11.13; Ze 4.1\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, nde kha nuianan, nde harigi Ňčgui gumgi fara muuŇčgiap kav, nde vh…®ra vhunaa fara muuŇčgiap fhura tuigap ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu khaŇč nde nzuai, nde wari won ndavi vuri vuzvugi mbat…®gi, nde k…®r nta seg…®ri. Mba t…®vi nde ndavi vherir kav, zazera nde nd…®knd…®gi phorga shogi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Mt 5.16; Ru 19.44; Ro 12.17; 2 Ko 8.21; Fi 2.15; Ta 2.8\x*Nde k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segi gumgi, nde mben r…®gar nzerara ruri. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip, buni mbat…®gir nde suanga, mbe zumgum nde mbui t…®vir vhuuiŇč gan…®v, mbe Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tugar, mbe Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Mt 22.21; Ro 13.1; Ta 3.1\x*Nde Guma Bak…®me nd…®knd…®g…®p, za mba Ňčgui gari gumgir pani piin k…®ri. Ňägui bak…®vi vh…®rve gari guman pan, ana guigira fharigi guma ma. Nde ana buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 14 Nde vh…®ra Ňčgui bak…®vi gari gumgir pani, nde vh…®ra mbe buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Mba Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani mbe ndi fegim, mbe kav, mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mbe zaagir mbe nd…®…®v, t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi, mbe mbe z…®ri ndi vun kuamkuarga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Ta 2.8; 1 Pi 2.12; 3.16\x*Fhe Bak…®me khuen nde vuzvugi, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. Nde t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčv, mba pham buni nzuav nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki fhuv gumgi, mbe buni mbat…®gir nde nzuai, nde mbe th…®ri p…®ngirga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt 1 Ko 7.22; Ga 5.1; 5.13\x*Nde b…®kb…®…®gi gumgi rui rurur muuŇčri. Nde mba rurur muuŇčv, nde khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…® thari, ‚ÄúNza ntigem b…®kb…®…®gi.‚ÄĚ Nde maaŇč suaŇčgip, nde mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir muunga. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nde Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaari gumgi kh…®ni rui rurur muuŇčri.
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Snd 24.21; Mt 22.21; Ro 12.10; Fi 2.3; Hi 13.1; 1 Pi 1.22\x*Nde t…®vir vhuuin za kha gumgir muuŇčri. Nde vh…®ra guigira wari won ndavir nza phorgav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®Ňčri. Nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me r…®v…®v anan piin k…®ri. Nde vh…®ra t…®vir vhuuin Ňčgui bak…®vi vh…®rve gari guman panan muuŇčri.
\s1 Nza Krais t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®p zaagi ndirga.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Ef 6.5; Kor 3.22; 1 T 6.1\x*Nde Ňčaara gumgi, nde wari wo gari mpiiŇčs…®gi piin k…®v, mbe nzuai buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Gu mba mpiiŇčs…®gi vhuuiŇčra gum mbarara nde nzuai mpiiŇčs…®gi piin k…®r zav nde nzuai fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nde mba vhav shi mpiiŇčs…®gi mbat…®gi, nde vh…®ra mbe piin k…®ri.
\v 19 AhaŇč, nde maaŇč muuŇčgip fhura Fhe Bak…®me gan…®rim, ana nde nd…®knd…®gi gan…®nga, nde Ňčgar…®rga. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip fhura zaagir nden n…®…®nga, nde mba zaagi ndirga, Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuun nden muunga.
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt 1 Pi 3.14; 3.17; 4.14-15\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®vi mbat…®gir muunga, mbe nta suaŇčv, nde shog…®rga, nde mba zaa ndirga, nde ne suaŇčv thag…®na big…®na ndigirie? Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®var vhuun muunga, mbe ne suaŇčv nde shog…®rga, nde mba zaa ndirga, Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuun nden muunga.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Mt 16.24; Zo 13.15; FG 14.22; 1 Pi 3.18; 1 Zo 2.6\x*Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®r zav nden kamgi. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Krais vh…®ra nden kurkura zav zaagi ndigi. Ana won t…®var nde kh…®vigi, nde mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Ais 53.9; Zo 8.46; 2 Ko 5.21; Hi 4.15\x*Ana t…®va mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgi fhu, ana vh…®ra buna thueŇč guigi fhu.
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Ais 53.7; Mt 27.39; Zo 8.48-49; Hi 12.3; 1 Pi 3.9\x*Mbe buni mbat…®gir ana nzuai, ana mbe buna mbat…®k thueŇč Ňčgarkarigi fhu. Ana zaa ndiav, ana mben farfa zav suaŇčgi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana wo ndi Fhe Bak…®me farve kh…®ngi. Ana nzerara za mba bigi ndiv th…®gar mbai guma ma.
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Ais 53.5; Ro 6.2; 6.11; 7.6; Hi 9.28\x*Krais, ana khanarareŇč ga ntorgap, ana nza muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana za ntan wo fhava phorgi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, nza mba t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza za nta tharga. Nza nta thav, nza k…®r…® t…®va vhuun muuŇčv, nza t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe hor mbat…®gar ana muuŇčgim, ana zaagi mbat…®gi ndigim, nza taagia nzerigi.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Ais 53.6; Ese 34.5-6; 34.23; Mt 9.36; Zo 10.14; Hi 13.20\x*Nde zam sipsivi fara muuŇčgip, fhura tamtam ruigi. Nde ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me taagia nde ndigim, nde zav wari wo vuavi han zegi. Nde vuavi tuituigia nden ntuu gari guma ma.
\c 3
\s1 Khe mani gu muuiaŇč r…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai buni khare.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Mt 18.15; 1 Ko 7.14-16; Ef 5.22; Kor 3.18; Ta 2.5\x*Mba t…®vara, nde mani ga r…®gi mbigi, nde wari wo manin piin k…®ri. Nden mani thari, mbe Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč z…®n vui fhu. Nde mben muuiŇč Fhe Bak…®me piin ki t…®vir vhuuiŇč, mbe nta gan…®p, nde buni tharir mbe suanga fhu, mbe ndavi dorg…®rga.
\v 2 Nde mben muuiŇč, mbe nde gari, nde nzerara ruav, guigira Fhe Bak…®me piin ki.
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 T 2.9; Ta 2.3\x*Nde vh…®ra fhura k…®rar wari wo fhavi s…®…®Ňčv, wari wo pani s…®…®Ňčv, nta far…®v, gorar muuŇčgi bigi s…®…®Ňčv, mbark…®rga shagi vhuuiŇč shar…® thari. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Sng 45.13; Ro 7.22; 2 Ko 4.16\x*Nde mbar…®gi fhuv s…®…®n wari wo ndavi vheri, nde nta s…®…®Ňčri. Mba s…®…®Ňč khare, ndav nzerara kav, ndav mb…®rav ki. Mba t…®v, ana Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man, ana t…®var vhuuŇč guar ma.
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 3:5-6 \xt Stt 18.12\x*Mba fhum kegi mbigi, mba mbiga mbe khare, Sara. Sara, ana wo ndiv Fhe Bak…®me n…®…®Ňčgiap, ana muun zav suaŇčgi bigi, ana ntan rarga ki. Mbe mba khesharigi t…®vir wari nz…®…®v, wari won mani piin ki. Sara Abraham nzuai buni z…®n vov, kha kakaman ana mbui, ‚ÄúGuman Rum‚ÄĚ. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčv, nde big…®n then riv…®rga fhu, nde Sarar Ňčkarmbigir fara muuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Ko 7.3; 12.23; Ef 5.25; Kor 3.19; 1 Te 4.4\x*Nde muuiŇč ga r…®gi gumgi, nde nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde tuituigip wari won muuiŇč phorg…®p piigip wari k…®ri. Mbigi, mben fhavi ŇčkasŇčkagi fhuvara, nde t…®var vhuuŇčra mben muuŇčri. Nde khaŇč muuŇčgip kaŇčgiri, mba mbigi, mbe vh…®ra zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndirga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip mba t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®rga, nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suanga, big…®n the nde ana phorga nzuai buni tuav puigi fhu.
\s1 Nza zazera t…®var vhuun harigi nt…®…®rir muuŇčri.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Mt 5.44; Ro 12.10; Fi 3.16; Kor 3.12; 1 Te 5.15; 1 Pi 2.17; 2.23\x*Gu ntigem kha buni vh…®z…® zav, gu khaŇč nzuai. Nde za wari t…®g…®p nd…®knd…®k ndava bavira k…®v, za kha gumgir korar muuŇčri. Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde guigira wari won ndavir wari wo phorge regi nt…®…®ri ga nd…®…®i t…®vara, nde wari won ndavir mben n…®…®Ňčv, guigira mben korar muuŇčv, r…®…®r…®…®i t…®vi thari.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Mt 25.34; Ro 12.14; 1 Te 5.15\x*Gumgi t…®vi mbat…®gir nden muuŇčrim, nde nta Ňčgarka thari. Mbe buni mbat…®gir nde suaŇčrim, nde mben buni mbat…®gi Ňčgarkav buni mbat…®gir mbe suaŇč thari. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nde kha t…®var mben t…®vi Ňčgarkari. Nde mbe suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana t…®var vhuun mben muuŇčri. Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®var muun zav nden kamgi. Nde nduarira ana Ňčg…®r kaman vhuuŇč ndirga.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Ze 1.26; 1 Pi 2.1; 2.22\x*\x - \xo 3:10 \xt Sng 34.12-16\x*Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai,
\q1 ‚ÄúGuma, ana mpirmpir…®ga t…®v nzerara k…®v, ana ndikndig…®p, tugir vhuuin k…®r saŇčv, ana buni mbat…®gi suaŇč thari, ana vh…®ra bigi guiguigi thari.
\q1 
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Ais 1.16-17; Ro 12.18; Hi 12.14\x*Ana wo k…®rar t…®vi mbat…®gi ga seg…®p, ana t…®vi vhuuiŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\q1 Ana harigi gumgi gu mbigi phorg…®p ndava bavira k…®v, ana khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\q1 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Zo 9.31\x*Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me, ana t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi garav, ana mbe ana phorga nzuai buni, ana khuarar nta r…®gi.
\q1 Guma Bak…®me, ana t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben vuzvugi gori.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Nza wari wo mbui t…®vir vhuuiaŇč nzuav zaagi ndi, ne nzerara.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Snd 16.7; Ro 8.28\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip t…®vi vhuuiŇč z…®n Ňčg…®rga, the t…®va mbat…®gar nden muuŇčgirie?
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Jer 1.8; Mt 5.10; Ze 1.12; 1 Pi 2.20; 4.14\x*\x - \xo 3:14 \xt Ais 8.12-13\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčv ne suaŇčv zaagi ndirga, nde ne suaŇčv ndikndig…®ri. Mbe r…®v…®rga big…®n thuen nden muuŇčrim, nde mben r…®v…® thari. Nde ne suaŇč Ňčgava mbat…®gar muuŇč thari. Zak…®ra Fhuvara!
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt FG 4.8; Kor 4.6; 2 T 2.25\x*Nde wari won ndavir vherir, nde Kraisra ndigiri, ana nden nd…®knd…®gir fhara k…®ri. Ana nde Bak…®me ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip, nde rarga ki big…®na vhuuŇč n…®…®Ňčge suaŇčv nden nzanga, nde zazera mben Ňčgarka saŇčv wari k…®ri.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Ta 2.8; Hi 13.18; 1 Pi 2.12\x*Nde zazera bunin vhuuiŇčra mben buni Ňčgarkav, mbarara mbe suaŇčri. Nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®man, nde nzerara wari k…®ri. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip buni mbat…®gir nde suaŇčv nde s…®…®nga. Nde Krais t…®var vhuuŇč z…®n vuim, nde nz…®…®i gumgi, mbe wari wo suaŇčgi buni mbat…®gi, mbe ntan mbergirga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Pi 2.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugirga, nza kha t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbuav ntan panan zaagi ndi, ne nzerara. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgip t…®vi mbat…®gir muuŇčv, ntan panan zaagi ndirga, ne guigira big…®na mbat…®geŇč ma.
\s1 Krais rimgiap, nza ndir zav taagia khavgi.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ro 5.6; 6.10; 8.11; 2 Ko 13.4; Ef 2.18; Kor 1.21-22\x*Nde vh…®ra Krais ga nd…®knd…®g…®. Ana t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n vui guma ma. Ana kha t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi Ňčana ndigap, ana t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®z…® zav rimgi. Ana rimgiap, nde ndiga Fhe Bak…®me han zi. Ana r…®mr…®m bueŇčra muuŇčgi, ana wom rimgirga fhu. Ana kha nuianan guma kim, mbe ana shogim, ana rimgi. Ana rimgiap, taagia khavgiap, Hevenan ndav, ana Ňčina fara muuŇčgiap ki.
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Stt 6.1‚Äď7.24; 8.18; Hi 11.7; 2 Pi 2.5\x*Ana Ňčina fara muuŇčgiap kav, ana vov, gumgi ntuu b…®nan ki Ňčgun vergap Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun mbe suaŇčgi. \f a \fr 3:19 \ft Bigi kaŇčgi gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui. Mba gumgi gu mbigir ntuu, mbe fhum Noa tugen vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigir ntuu ma. Mbe mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Ana mba Fhe Bak…®me kaadogi ŇčiniŇčgi o, Fhe Bak…®me enseri ga nzuai. Mbe ZudaiŇč khueŇč khoth…®gi. Mbe gumgi gu mbigir ntuu, mbe Noa tugen vh…®zgim, Fhe Bak…®me mbe ndim phena t…®vaneŇč ga suegi nt…®…®ri ma. \f*
\v 20 Mba gumgi, mbe fhum Noa tugen, mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaadogi. Noa kegi tugen, t…®vi mbat…®gi guigira k…®vgi, Fhe Bak…®me vhemkora nen vhezar mbe n…®…®Ňčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana Noan rarga kim, ana za won kema bak…®me muuŇčgia thugi. Ana won kema bak…®me muuŇčgia thugim, harath…®gi gumgira, mbe mba kema bak…®me vhen vergim, mb…® bak…®me vhuuŇčgia ndav, mbe kh…®ga mba kema fegim, Fhe Bak…®me taagiap mbe ndigim, mbe nzerara ki.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Ro 10.10; Ef 5.26; Ta 3.5; Hi 10.22\x*Mba mb…®, ana nza ndavi dorgap Fhe Bak…®me z…®n panan ruai, nen panpana rugi. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nza Fhe Bak…®me mb…®n panan, ana taagia nza ndigi. Nza ana z…®n panan ruagi ruar…®, mba ruar…®, ana nzan fhava nzaŇčnzaŇč ruai ruar…® fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mba ruar…®, nza Fhe Bak…®me phorgap khaŇč nzuai ruar…® ma. Nza ana r…®mani n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®rga. Nza ana z…®n panan ruagi ruar…®, Fhe Bak…®me taagia nza ndir zav, ne nzuav Zisas Krais rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgi. \f b \fr 3:21 \ft Kha vezar Grikar kaman kha kameŇč tuituigiap h…®gi fhuvara. \f*
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Sng 110.1; Mt 22.44; Ro 8.34; 8.38; 1 Ko 15.24; Ef 1.20-21\x*Ana ana khavgim, ana ntigem Hevenan ndagi. Ana ndav, ntigem ana Fhe Bak…®me guva hareŇč ga perav mbur ki. Ntigem mba Fhe Bak…®me enseri gum, mba ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me ki ŇčiniŇčgi, mba ŇčkasŇčka ki bigi zam, mbe ana piin ki. \fig Krais kha nuianan ana guma guara gegap kim, mbe ana shogim, ana rimgiap, khavgiap, ana ntigem Hevenan ana Ňčinan fara muuŇčgiap ki. (3.21) |src="HK-29A.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="3.21"\fig*
\c 4
\ms1 Mparmpara Bak…®me guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgir him, mbe zaagi ndi.
\s1 Nza won ndavi vuri t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…® thari.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Ro 6.2; 6.7; Ga 5.24; Kor 3.3-5\x*Krais, ana won fhavara ana zaagi ndigi. Nde ana suirigi nd…®knd…®gara suirari. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, guma maaŇč muuŇčgip, ana won fhavara zaagi ndigirga, ana t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui t…®va tharga. \f a \fr 4:1 \ft Zaa ndi t…®va nzuai buni mbari vh…®ra I Pita 3:13 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p 22 th…®g…®ri. \f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Zo 1.13; Ro 6.11; 2 Ko 5.15; Ga 2.20; 1 Zo 2.16\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip Ňčamra k…®v, nde won vuzvugi z…®n Ňčg…®rga fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nde Fhe Bak…®men vuzvugara z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt FG 17.30; Ef 2.2-3; 4.17; Ta 3.3\x*Nde za ndava vura t…®vi z…®n vegap, mba Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi guigira vuzvugap, mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde nta muuŇčgi. Mba t…®vi khare, gumgi gu mbigi ruarir wari ndi, t…®vi mbat…®gi ga nzuav ndavi khavi, pharar ŇčanŇčani pi, shaa bak…®vi ga mbuav mba k…®vgia pav, k…®vgiap pharar ŇčanŇčani pav t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daasuav, mbar…®vi gu tori guigira t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira mbuav, ntan rotu mbui.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt FG 13.45; 18.6; 1 Pi 3.16\x*Nde ntigem, nde Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi phorgap feiŇč gu daa nd…®knd…®gi nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui fhu. Nde nta mbui fhuv, mbe mba t…®va gangiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, mbe buni mbat…®gir nde nzuai.
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt FG 10.42; 17.31; 1 Ko 15.51-52; Ze 5.9\x*Mbe zumgum, mbe nduarira Fhe Bak…®me n…®ma thivgip, mbe wo muuŇčgi t…®vi, mbe nta bun ana suanga. Mba t…®vi ga nzuav nzuai guma, mbe suan zav mben rarga mbur ki. Ana Ňčamki gumgi mbui t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga, ana vh…®ra vh…®zgi gumgi muuŇčgi t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga.
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Ro 8.10; 1 Ko 5.5\x*Mba buna n…®…®eŇčra nzuav Krais rimgiap, ana vov, mba vh…®zgi gumgi ki Ňčgun vergap, won buna vhuueŇč bun mbe suaŇčgi. KhueŇč guigi guarara, kha nuianan ki gumgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgiap, mbe za vh…®z…®rga, mbe mba t…®va muuŇčgiap vh…®zgi. Mbe ntigem Krais won buna vhuueŇč bun mbe suaŇčgim, mbe ne khoth…®gap, mbe zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigap, mbe ŇčiniŇčgi ga gegap, mbe Fhe Bak…®me ki fara muuŇčgiap wari ki. \f b \fr 4:6 \ft KhaŇč mbe Grikar kaman suaŇčgi kameŇč, kha vezar tuituigiap h…®gi fhuvara. Mbe gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Ana kha nzuai kameŇč ne sapta 3 ves 19 fara muuŇčgi. Mbe ne domdorav khaŇč nzuai. ‚ÄúMba big…®na n…®…®eŇčra nzuav, Zisas Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčgi. Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za kha gumgi gu mbigi vh…®zgi t…®vara muuŇčgiap vh…®zgi. Mbe wari wo muuŇčgi t…®vir mbat…®gir vheza ndigi. Ana vov, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe suaŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip ana buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®g…®rga, mbe zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigip, mben ntuu Fhe Bak…®men Ňčina ki farar muuŇčgip k…®rga.‚ÄĚ \f*
\s1 Nza Fhe Bak…®me fhura nza n…®…®Ňčgi nd…®knd…®gir vhuuiŇč, nza tuituigira ntan Ňčgar…®ri.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 24.13-14; Ru 21.34; Ro 13.11-12; 1 Ko 10.11; Fi 4.5; Kor 4.2; 2 Pi 3.9; 1 Zo 2.18\x*Kha bigi za vh…®z…®rga tuk han mbarigi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde tuituigip nd…®knd…®g…®p, tuituigip wari wo mbui t…®vi gan…®v, nde tuituigip Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suanga.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Snd 10.12; 1 Ko 13.7; Kor 3.14; Hi 13.1; Ze 5.20; 1 Pi 1.22\x*Kha t…®vi za nta kharav farigi t…®v khare, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde guigira wari won ndavir mben n…®…®Ňčv, mba t…®v, nde guigira ana suirav havhargiri. Mba t…®v khaŇč muuŇčgi, harigi guma t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®rver nde muuŇčgi, nde za nta mbevav, nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangiri. Mba t…®v, ana mba harigi t…®vi, kambarigi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt 2 Ko 9.7; Fi 2.14; Fm 1.14; Hi 13.2\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi thari z…®v, nden han k…®rim, nde tuituigip mbe gan…®ri. Nde mba Ňčaarar muuŇčv, nde ne suaŇčv, ndavi mbar…®g…® thari.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Ro 12.6-8; 1 Ko 4.1-2; 4.7; Ta 1.7\x*Nde bevbevira Fhe Bak…®me nde kora muuŇčgiap, ana fhura mba nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin gum ana won Ňčaarir muun zav n…®…®Ňčgi ŇčkasŇčkagir nde n…®…®Ňčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde bevbevira, nde Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaara gumgir vhuuiŇč k…®v, mba nd…®knd…®gir vhuuin, nde warira kurkurari.
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt 1 Ko 3.10; 10.31; Ef 5.20; 1 Pi 5.11; VB 1.6\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun suanga nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč ndigi, ana guigira Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇčra bun suaŇčri. Guma gumgir kurkurigi, ana Fhe Bak…®me ana nd…®…®i ŇčkasŇčkar, ana khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, mba Ňčaarar muuŇčri. Nde maaŇč muuŇčrim, harigi gumgi nde mbui bigi gan…®nga. Mbe nde gan…®v, Zisas Kraisan z…®n panan mbe Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Ana z…® bak…®me gum ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki. Ne guigi guarara.
\s1 Nza Krais zaagi ndigi mbugum, zaagi ndirga ne suaŇčv ndikndig…®rga.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt 1 Ko 3.13; 1 Pi 1.6-7\x*Nde guigira na phorgap Zisas Krais khoth…®gi gumgi, nde ntigem mparmpare vhav nde shi fara muuŇčgiap nde shirga. Nde ne suaŇčv Ňčgava mbat…®gar muuŇčgip, khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi thari, khe harigi khesharigi t…®v nzan hi. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt FG 5.41; Ro 8.17; 2 Ko 1.7; 2 T 2.12; Ze 1.2; 1 Pi 1.5-6; VB 1.9\x*Nde mba mparmpare nden hi, nde Krais ndigi zaagi, nde nta ndi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap nde ndikndig…®ri. Zumgum Krais z…® bak…®me za k…®rar h…®rga, nde guigira ndikndiga mbat…®gar muuŇčv, nde ndavi nzerav k…®rga.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Sng 89.50-51; Mt 5.11; 2 Ko 12.10; Ze 1.12; 1 Pi 2.20\x*Nde Krais z…® suirigim, ana nden ki, mbe ne suaŇčv buni mbat…®gir nde suav nde s…®…®Ňčrim, nde ne suaŇčv ndikndig…®ri. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar, ana z…® bak…®me gum ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me ki, mba Ňäina Ňäaar nden ki.
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt 1 Te 4.11; 1 T 5.13; 1 Pi 2.20\x*Nde tuituigira wari gan…®ri, nde muuŇčv k…®v guma the shogirim, ana rimgi o, bigi thari k…®mgirga o, harigi khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgi o, harigi guman Ňčaara farfagi, mbe mba bigi ga suaŇčv zaagir nden n…®…®nga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt FG 11.26; Fi 1.20\x*Guma ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, ana ne nzuav zaagi ndi, ana ne suaŇčv mber…® thari. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nen z…® ndi, ana nen ndikndig…®ri. Ana nen ndikndig…®p Fhe Bak…®men z…® ndiv vun kuamkuari.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Jer 25.29; Mal 3.5; Ru 10.12-14; 23.31; 2 Te 1.8\x*Fhe Bak…®me, nza ana nt…®…®ri, ana nza muuŇčgi t…®vi ga suaŇčv nza suanga tuk, ana h…®gi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nza fharav ana n…®ma thiv…®rga, mba Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč daasui gumgi, mbe ana n…®ma thiv…®rga, ana mbe muuŇčgi t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga, mbe buni ram mbui vh…®za t…®var muuŇčgirie?
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Snd 11.31; Ru 23.31\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgip, mba t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi mbe Ňčaara mbat…®gara muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®me taagip mbe ndirga tuav k…®rga. Mba k…®r Fhe Bak…®me ga segap, t…®vi mbat…®gi mbui gumgi ram muuŇčgirie?‚ÄĚ
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt Sng 31.5; Ru 23.46; 2 T 1.12\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®me vuzvuk ma. Ana gumgi thari vuzvugi mbe zaagi ndirga, mba gumgi mbe wari ndiv Fhe Bak…®me farve kh…®ngip, mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muuŇčri. Fhe Bak…®me nza muuŇčgiap, ana zazera tuituigira nza gari.
\c 5
\s1 Nde Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi nde tuituigira mbe gan…®ri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt FG 1.8; 1.22; Ro 8.17-18; VB 1.9\x*Gu ntigem nde sios gari gumgir pani, gu nde suan za mbui. Gu vh…®ra nde mbui Ňčaarara mbui. Gu vh…®ra won r…®manira, gu Krais garim, ana zaa ndigi. Gu zumgum nza zam wari t…®g…®ra mba Fhe Bak…®me nzan n…®…®n za suaŇčgi bigir vhuuiŇč, Krais ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me gu z…® bak…®me zumgum za k…®rar h…®g…®rga, nza mba bigi ndirga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde sios gari gumgir pani, gu maaŇč muun zav nde nzuai.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Zo 10.11-13; 21.15-17; FG 20.28; 1 Ko 9.17; 1 T 3.3; 3.8; Ta 1.7; 1.11; Fm 1.14\x*Nde tuituigira guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi gan…®ri. Mbe sipsivi fara muuŇčgiap nden farven ki. Nde Fhe Bak…®me nde vuzvugi t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®p mba Ňčaarar muuŇčv, nde nen ndikndig…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®v, harigi nt…®…®ri vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®p, mba Ňčaarar muunga. Nde vh…®ra vhezara suaŇčv mba Ňčaarar muuŇč thari. Fhuvara. Nde guigira mba Ňčaarar muunga vuzvuk k…®v, mba Ňčaarar muuŇčri.
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Sng 74.2; 1 Ko 3.9; 2 Ko 1.24; Fi 3.17; 1 T 4.12; Ta 2.7\x*Nde gumgi ruu farar muuŇčgip k…®v mba Fhe Bak…®me nde farve kh…®ngi gumgi gu mbigi, nde mbe mbev…®v, mbe kharav, vun k…® thari. Fhuvara. Nde t…®var vhuuŇčra muuŇčrim, mbe mba t…®va gan…®v, nde z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt 1 Ko 9.25; 2 T 4.8; Hi 13.20; 1 Pi 1.4\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip mba t…®var muunga, mba Sipsivi Gari Guman Vhari Krais, ana za k…®rar h…®g…®rga, nde ne suaŇčv, fharigi vheza vhuuŇč guarara ndigirga. Mba vhez, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki vhez ma, ana mbar…®gi vhez fhuvara.
\s1 Nza wari ndiv Fhe Bak…®me farve kh…®ngiri.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Snd 3.34; Ais 57.15; Ef 5.21; Fi 2.3; Ze 4.6\x*Mba t…®vara, nde gumgir Ňčkaa, nde wari won gumgir pani piin k…®ri. Nde za kha t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nde za wari mbevav, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi piin k…®ri. Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me wari wo z…®ri ndi vunfi gumgi, ana mbe z…®ri mbevi. Ana wo z…®ri mbevi gumgi, ana mbe kora mbuav, t…®var vhuuŇčra mbe mbui.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Mt 23.12; Ru 14.11; 18.14; Ze 4.10\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde wari wo vuzvugi mbevav, nde Fhe Bak…®me hara ŇčkasŇčkani piin k…®ri. Nde k…®v k…®rim, ana wo sarigi tugara, ana nde suirav nde vun feg…®rga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Sng 37.5; 55.22; Mt 6.25-30; Fi 4.6\x*Fhe Bak…®me nde kora mbui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde mba ndi simt…®gi, nde nta ndiv, ana farve ga suri.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Ru 22.31; 1 Te 5.6; VB 12.12\x*Nde tuituigira wari gan…®v, anan rarg…® k…®ri. Nden pana guma Satan, ana raion bak…®me fara muuŇčgiap davav, mbur vov, khar zav ki. Ana zazera gumgi gu mbigir farfa zav mbe nzuav garav ki.
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt FG 14.22; Ef 6.11-13; 2 T 3.12; Ze 4.7\x*Nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Zisas khoth…®g…®p, Satan daaŇčgi mbur kh…®ngiri. Nde kaŇčgi, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve kha nuianan ki. Mbe vh…®ra nde ndi simt…®gira ndi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt 2 Ko 4.17; 1 Te 2.12; 2 Te 2.17; 1 T 6.12; Hi 13.21; 1 Pi 1.6\x*Fhe Bak…®me ana mbark…®rga kora muumbara, ana za ntan n…®…®Ňčge ma. Ana Krais Zisasan z…®n panan, ana nden kamgi. Nde ana phorg…®p, ana ŇčkasŇčka vhuuŇč bak…®me, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki, nde ana phorg…®p, anan vhen k…®rga. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde tuga t…®vaneŇčra, nde zaa ndigirga. Ana zumgum nden muuŇčgirim, nde nzerarga. Nde ana khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k, ana anan havhargip, nden kurarim, nde nd…®knd…®gi havhargip, nde zazera th…®g…® havhargirga.
\v 11 Ana nduara zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki ŇčkasŇčka ki. Ne guigira guarara.
\s1 Buni mbariveŇč khare.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt FG 15.22; 15.40; 2 Ko 1.19; 1 Te 1.1; Hi 13.22; 2 Pi 1.12\x*Gu kha buniveŇč nzuaim, Sairas nta khergi. Gu ana garim, ana guigira nza phorgap Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Gu kha gavar, gu Fhe Bak…®me nde kora mbuav won kora muumbarar nde kh…®vav, nde mbui t…®vi bun nde suan za mbui. Ana nduara zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki ŇčkasŇčka ki. Ne guigi guarara. Gu nduara ana kora muumbara guar, gu ana kaŇčgi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana bun nzuai. Gu nde ndavi havhar…®rgeŇč nzuav nde nzuai. Nde guigira th…®g…® havhargip, ana khoth…®g…®ri.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; 13.13; 15.37-39; Kor 4.10; 2 T 4.11; Fm 1.24\x*Mba Babironan guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mba gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me mben nde phorga ruegi, mbe wari won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. Nan kam Mak, ana vh…®ra won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Ro 16.16; 1 Ko 16.20; Ef 6.23\x*Nde zam mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde mben harir suig…®p, mbe viav…®v, mbe Ňčkor pan…®ri. Nde mba t…®var mben muunga, mbe kaŇčgi, nde guigira mbe vuzvugiap, wari won ndavir mbe nd…®…®i.
\p Nde guigira Krais phorgi, nde ndavi mb…®rav wari k…®ri.
